417
00:28:23,800 --> 00:28:26,000
Dino, rượu whiskey.

418
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:30,000
Whiskey.

419
00:28:33,360 --> 00:28:35,320
Xin lỗi, chúng tôi muốn rượu whiskey.

